iveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511033910/http://www.tonyawards.com/en_US/nominees/index.html |archivedate=11 May 2008}}</ref>\n|''Macbeth''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2009\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actor in a Miniseries or a Movie]]\n|''[[Hamlet (2009 television film)|Hamlet]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Laurence Olivier Award for Best Performance in a Supporting Role]]\n|''Hamlet''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Ride of Fame]]: Immortal<ref>[http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20131204/hells-kitchen-clinton/patrick-stewart-honored-with-broadway-themed-tour-bus Patrick Stewart Honored With Broadway-Themed Tour Bus] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930194217/http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20131204/hells-kitchen-clinton/patrick-stewart-honored-with-broadway-themed-tour-bus |date=30 September 2015 }}. DNAinfo. 4 December 2013</ref>\n| \u2014\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|2016\n|[[Golden Globe Award for Best Actor - Television Series Musical or Comedy]]\n| ''[[Blunt Talk]]''\n|{{nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2017\n|[[2017 Fangoria Chainsaw Awards|Fangoria Chainsaw Award]] for Best Supporting Actor<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.fangotv.com/the-2017-fangoria-chainsaw-awards-winners-and-full-results/ |title=The 2017 FANGORIA Chainsaw Awards Winners and Full Results! |work=FANGORIA\u00ae |accessdate=30 August 2018}}</ref>\n| ''[[Green Room (film)|Green Room]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|[[San Diego International Film Festival#Gregory Peck Award|Gregory Peck Award]] ([[San Diego International Film Festival]])\n|\u2014\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|Legends of Cinema Award ([[Savannah College of Art and Design#Savannah Film Festival|Savannah Film Festival]])<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.islandpacket.com/entertainment/arts-culture/article175458016.html |title=Patrick Stewart will be at Savannah Film Fest. Here are the other celebs being honored |work=islandpacket |accessdate=10 October 2018}}</ref>\n|\u2014\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Detroit Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actor]]\n|''[[Logan (film)|Logan]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2018\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Supporting Actor]] \n|''Logan''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Supporting Actor]]\n|''Logan''\n| {{won}}\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"n\"}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* {{cite journal |last=Schulman |first=Michael |date=15 November 2010 |title=The Talk of the Town: The Boards: Roommates |journal=[[The New Yorker]] |volume=86 |issue=36 |pages=36\u2013? |url=http://www.newyorker.com/talk/2010/11/15/101115ta_talk_schulman |accessdate=28 January 2012}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*{{NPG name}}\n* {{IBDB name|09608}}\n* {{Iobdb name|2983}}\n* {{IMDb name|1772}}\n* {{Tcmdb name}}\n* {{Allmovie name|68265}}\n* [http://www.emmys.com/celebrities/patrick-stewart Patrick Stewart at Emmys.com]\n\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards for Patrick Stewart\n|list =\n{{DramaDesk One-Person Show 1984\u20132000}}\n{{Evening Standard Theatre Award for Best Actor}} \n{{OlivierAward PlaySupportingPerformance}}\n{{Saturn Award for Best Supporting Actor}}\n}}\n{{People's Vote}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Stewart, Patrick}}\n[[Category:1940 births]]\n[[Category:20th-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century English male actors]]\n[[Category:Academics of the University of Huddersfield]]\n[[Category:Actors awarded knighthoods]]\n[[Category:Advocates of the European Union]]\n[[Category:Alumni of Bristol Old Vic Theatre School]]\n[[Category:Audiobook narrators]]\n[[Category:Drama Desk Award winners]]\n[[Category:English anti\u2013Iraq War activists]]\n[[Category:English expatriates in the United States]]\n[[Category:English feminists]]\n[[Category:English male film actors]]\n[[Category:English male Shakespearean actors]]\n[[Category:English male stage actors]]\n[[Category:English male television actors]]\n[[Category:English male video game actors]]\n[[Category:English male voice actors]]\n[[C